<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Nov 2021 09:38:23 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>大欖郊野公園木糠廁所，網民組隊去大便、擔心廁紙不可沖走</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/RRNXnAjuzPc/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 10 Nov 2021 09:37:31 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[大欖郊野公園]]></category><category><![CDATA[木糠廁所]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1070539</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>漁護署為香港引入免沖水木糠廁所，收集遊客的排泄物與木糠混合後再轉化為肥料。而全港首個木糠廁所設置於大欖郊野公園 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>漁護署為香港引入免沖水木糠廁所，收集遊客的排泄物與木糠混合後再轉化為肥料。而全港首個木糠廁所設置於大欖郊野公園，並在數日前起開放進行試驗。但由於此類廁所毋須（沒有）沖水，有網民就擔心衛生問題，也擔心廁紙不能掉入廁所，極不衛生。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/248044062_4480384482052287_5749544125425038833_n-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1070546" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/248044062_4480384482052287_5749544125425038833_n-1.jpg" alt="" width="526" height="395" /></a></p><p>為解決偏遠郊野公園因缺水缺電，而無法設置沖水廁所的問題，漁護署於香港郊野公園 Facebook 專頁中表示，參考了外國的例子，於大欖郊野公園設置首個木糠廁所，以解決遊客的需要。木糠廁所分為上下兩層，漁護署指上層為廁所，會將排泄物收集及儲存於廁所下層，而排泄物及木糠會定時由太陽能推動的摩打攪拌。為確保混合物保持在合適的溫度及濕度中，廁所下層亦有設置加熱保器，令混合物更容易被生物帶氧分解，能減低臭味及有助轉化為肥料。漁護署亦提醒市民，使用時切勿將廁紙等的垃圾扔進木糠廁所，以阻礙排泄物分解。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-09-下午 6.56.57.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070544" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-09-下午 6.56.57-441x580.png" alt="" width="441" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-09-下午 6.56.57-441x580.png 441w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-09-下午 6.56.57-685x900.png 685w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-09-下午 6.56.57-768x1009.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-09-下午 6.56.57.png 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 441px" /></a></p><p>漁護處屬下的「香港郊野公園」Facebook 專頁下有網民留言支持，形容計劃既環保又衛生，值得推廣，有網民話「搵日特登約埋一班朋友，輪住去痾屎體驗下」。亦有網民擔憂「塞廁」問題，更指出衛生及氣味問題。有網民查詢清潔身體時用到的廁紙是否能掉入廁所，FB 小編就指廁紙及其他物品都不可掉落去，要使用廁所內的垃圾箱，有網民就表示這樣會令垃圾桶「勁臭」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖_2021-11-10_17_31_14.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1070689" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖_2021-11-10_17_31_14.jpg" alt="" width="389" height="91" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖_2021-11-10_17_30_37.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070691" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖_2021-11-10_17_30_37-405x580.jpg" alt="" width="405" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖_2021-11-10_17_30_37-405x580.jpg 405w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖_2021-11-10_17_30_37.jpg 482w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 405px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-10-17.30.37.jpg"><br /></a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/hongkongcountryparks/videos/1447455412314753/">香港郊野公園 Facebook 專頁</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></p></p><div class="feedflare">
